<div class="feed-main">
<div class="content">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/42094770" target="_blank" data-id="9045716" data-za-element-name="Title">
前端使用面向对象式编程 还是 函数式编程 针对什么问题用什么方式 分别有什么具体案例？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/42094770/answer/93689490">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="32916301">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="93689490"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>99</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="count">99</span>
<span class="label sr-only">赞同</span>
</button>
<button class="down ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="label sr-only">反对</span>
</button>
</div>



<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">

<span class="summary-wrapper">
<span class="author-link-line">

<a class="author-link"
data-hovercard="p$t$livoras.com"
target="_blank" href="/people/livoras.com"
>戴嘉华</a></span><span title="请不要再邀请我回答关于前端的问题，谢谢。https://github.com/livoras" class="bio">
请不要再邀请我回答关于前端的问题，谢谢。…
</span>
</span>
