<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/41922432" target="_blank" data-id="8976498" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何评价 Webpack 2 新引入的 Tree-shaking 代码优化技术？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/41922432/answer/93068390">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="32666959">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="93068390"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>99</a>
