<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/31863910" target="_blank" data-id="4944809" data-za-element-name="Title">
有关javascript函数对象？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/31863910/answer/53626472">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="16856126">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="53626472"> -->

