<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/27791075" target="_blank" data-id="3299373" data-za-element-name="Title">
vue，angular，avalon这三种MVVM框架之间有什么优缺点？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/27791075/answer/38830138">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="10923970">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="38830138"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>99</a>
